# ---------- docs/ allowlist ----------
# Planning artifacts (master plan, phase blueprints, todos, scratch notes)
# live in this folder but are NOT tracked by git. The folder is allowlist-only:
# ignore everything by default, then explicitly opt-in files that should be
# committed by adding them below.

# Ignore everything in this folder by default
*

# Always allow this file itself (otherwise the allowlist rules disappear,
# and this file also anchors the folder for fresh clones)
!.gitignore

# Allowlist tracked docs here as they are ready to be committed.
# Examples (uncomment / add as needed):
# !ARCHITECTURE.md
# !INSTALL.md

# README assets — screenshots + logo + wordmark renders + SVG sources.
!assets/
!assets/**
